英國時間2021年4月9日早上，[[爱丁堡公爵菲利普亲王|菲臘親王愛丁堡公爵]]去世，享耆壽99歲。他是[[英国君主|英国君主]][[伊丽莎白二世|伊丽莎白二世]]的[[王夫|王夫]]，白金漢宮證實其死因為衰老導致的自然死亡。

菲利普親王有權接受[[受国葬的人士列表|国葬]]，但他生前即表示不希望對公眾造成騷擾<ref name="smh">{{cite web|title=Prince Philip dies in Windsor Castle aged 99|url=https://www.smh.com.au/world/europe/prince-philip-dies-in-windsor-castle-aged-99-20200205-p53y58.html|accessdate=2021-04-09|date=2021-04-09|last=Shields|first=Bevan|work=[[雪梨晨鋒報|The Sydney Morning Herald]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412065850/https://www.smh.com.au/world/europe/prince-philip-dies-in-windsor-castle-aged-99-20200205-p53y58.html|archive-date=2021-04-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="operationforthbridge">{{cite web|last=Traynor|first=Sian|date=2021-02-22|title=Everything that will happen in 'Operation Forth Bridge' when Prince Philip dies|url=https://www.edinburghlive.co.uk/news/uk-world-news/operation-forth-bridge-everything-happen-19889779|access-date=2021-04-09|website=Edinburgh Live|archive-date=2021-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409112453/https://www.edinburghlive.co.uk/news/uk-world-news/operation-forth-bridge-everything-happen-19889779|dead-url=no}}</ref>，希望在[[圣乔治礼拜堂_(温莎城堡)|聖喬治禮拜堂]]舉行一場{{tsl|en|military funeral|軍事葬禮}}，並奉厝於該禮拜堂內的皇家墓室，以待未來女王駕崩後再一同下葬於[[聖喬治禮拜堂|聖喬治禮拜堂]]的喬治六世紀念禮拜堂（King George VI Memorial Chapel）<ref name=operationforthbridge/>。葬礼于4月17日举行，[[白金漢宮|白金漢宮]]依照現今英國防疫規範，將葬禮參與者人數限制為30名<ref name="BBCFuneral">{{Cite news |date=2021-04-10 |title=Prince Philip: Funeral to take place on 17 April |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56702886 |access-date=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414115007/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56702886 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 福斯橋行動 ==

菲臘親王逝世後，英國政府啟動「福斯橋行動」。計劃包括[[白金漢宮|白金漢宮]]同時向[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]（BBC）和{{tsl|en|PA Media|新聞協會 (英國)|新聞協會}}發布新聞稿，協議假定[[宮務大臣|宮務大臣]]在新聞稿發布之前已與女王協商。同時，[[英國國旗|英國國旗]]將於全國哀悼期間[[下半旗|下半旗]]。哀悼期間，所有電視節目主持人都必須穿著黑色服飾<ref name="operationforthbridge"/>。哀悼期為八日，期間不會通過任何法律。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Mosalski|first=Ruth|date=2021-04-09|title=Operation Forth Bridge: What happens now after Prince Philip's death|url=https://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/local-news/operation-forth-bridge-what-happens-12928762|access-date=2021-04-09|website=WalesOnline|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418063121/https://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/uk-news/operation-forth-bridge-what-happens-12928762|dead-url=no}}</ref>

BBC等媒体第一时间做出了应对。BBC的电视频道當時播放的節目被數秒的黑畫面打斷，在发布王室声明前打出了写有“News Report”（新闻报道）的黑白字卡，随后由BBC新闻主播{{le|玛蒂娜·克罗克索尔|Martine Croxall}}身着黑衣、语带哽咽地向观众宣布菲利普亲王的死讯，并播放英国国歌《[[天佑女王|天佑女王]]》，同时播放爱丁堡公爵纹章及菲利普亲王遗像；除[[CBBC|CBBC]]和[[CBeebies|CBeebies]]之外的BBC电视频道并机播出至当地时间当天18:00。BBC广播节目被英国国歌打断，随后也改为播出较为低沉的音乐。其它英国媒体也有类似的安排。<ref>{{Citation|title=BBC interrupt programming to announce the death of Prince Philip. (BBC One)|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8I3mu-MG_J4|accessdate=2021-04-14|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414160029/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8I3mu-MG_J4|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 葬礼 ==
=== 游行与教堂仪式 ===
菲利普亲王因其生前遺願，後事一切從簡，未依照極高階王室成員的喪禮接受{{tsl|en|State funerals in the United Kingdom|英国国葬|国葬}}，改接受皇家仪式葬礼<ref name="BBC-service">{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56694327 |title=Prince Philip: What are the plans for his funeral? |work=BBC News |date=2021-04-10 |access-date=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417100835/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56694327 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。亲王生前希望丧礼从简，故不设{{tsl|en|lie in state|吊唁仪式}}<ref name="smh" /><ref name="operationforthbridge" />，但礼拜开始前，靈柩安奉於温莎城堡私人教堂<ref>{{Cite news |date=2021-04-09 |title=Prince Philip has died aged 99, Buckingham Palace announces |work=BBC News |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-11437314 |access-date=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417181019/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-11437314 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。仪式开始前，亲王的灵柩从教堂移到城堡内厅<ref>{{cite news|last=Specia|first=Megan|date=2021-04-17|title=Prince Philip’s Funeral: Latest Updates|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/04/17/world/prince-philip-funeral|access-date=2021-04-17|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417182139/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/04/17/world/prince-philip-funeral|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亲王曾有意在[[圣乔治礼拜堂_(温莎城堡)|圣乔治礼拜堂]]举行{{tsl|en|military funeral|军事丧礼}}，安葬于[[浮若閣摩爾|浮若閣摩爾]]，同时圣乔治堂的仪式采用更为传统的风格<ref name="operationforthbridge" />。此前[[伊莉莎白王太后|伊莉莎白王太后]]和[[威爾斯王妃戴安娜|威爾斯王妃戴安娜]]也曾接受皇家仪式葬礼<ref name="valentine">{{Cite news |last1=Low |first1=Valentine |title=Prince Philip funeral plans: what happens next after his death |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/prince-philip-funeral-plans-what-happens-next-after-his-death-hz3fs235b |access-date=2021-04-09 |work=The Times |date=2021-04-09 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417202234/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/prince-philip-funeral-plans-what-happens-next-after-his-death-hz3fs235b |dead-url=no }}</ref>。仪式被电视直播，英国广播公司出动电视[[英国广播公司第一台|第一台]]、[[英国广播公司新闻频道|新闻台]]，以及广播[[BBC廣播四台|四台]]和{{le|BBC广播五台|BBC Radio 5 Live|五台}}现场直播丧礼实况<ref name=bbcfuneralcoverage>{{cite web|last=Spyro|first=Steph|date=2021-04-17|title=Millions of viewers around world to watch as Britain falls silent in honour of Duke|url=https://www.express.co.uk/news/uk/1424271/prince-philip-funeral-duke-britain-silent-world-royal-viewers|access-date=2021-04-17|website=Express|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417192003/https://www.express.co.uk/news/uk/1424271/prince-philip-funeral-duke-britain-silent-world-royal-viewers|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另外[[独立电视台|独立电视台]]、[[天空新闻台|天空新闻台]]、[[天空第一台|天空第一台]]也有转播<ref name=bbcfuneralcoverage/>。[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]、[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]、[[福斯新闻频道|福斯新闻频道]]、[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]和[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]]在美国同步直播丧礼<ref name=bustlefuneral>{{cite web|title=Here’s How To Watch Prince Philip’s Funeral In The US|url=https://www.bustle.com/entertainment/how-to-watch-prince-philips-funeral-in-the-us|access-date=2021-04-17|website=Bustle|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415163602/https://www.bustle.com/entertainment/how-to-watch-prince-philips-funeral-in-the-us|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="insiderfuneral">{{cite web |last1=Humphries |first1=Monica |title=Prince Philip's funeral service is airing this weekend — here's how to watch |url=https://www.insider.com/how-to-watch-prince-philips-funeral-service-us-uk-viewers-2021-4 |website=Insider |access-date=2021-04-17 |date=2021-04-15 |archive-date=2021-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418063128/https://www.insider.com/how-to-watch-prince-philips-funeral-service-us-uk-viewers-2021-4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

仪式前，军乐团游行进入温莎城堡四方院（Quadrangle），沿途吹奏乐曲《[[耶路撒冷_(讚歌)|耶路撒冷]]》、《[[祖国我向你立誓|祖国我向你立誓]]》、《Supreme Sacrifice》、《Isle of Beauty》和《Nimrod》<ref>{{Cite news|title=Military bands pay tribute to Prince Philip|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/av/uk-56788553|access-date=2021-04-17|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417181125/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/av/uk-56788553|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[File:Royal_Standard_of_Prince_Philip,_Duke_of_Edinburgh.svg|left]]，右上为[[希腊国徽|希腊国徽]]、左下为[[蒙巴顿家族|蒙巴顿家族]]纹章，右下为{{tsl|en|Coat of arms of Edinburgh|爱丁堡徽章}}<ref name="BBC-service" />。]]
丧礼于4月17日举行，扶灵的[[掷弹兵卫队|掷弹兵卫队]]从温莎城堡大入口进入圣乔治礼拜堂，将灵柩放在西侧台阶（West Steps）。扶灵卫兵身穿[[橄榄绿|橄榄绿]]，行军事仪式，乘坐亲王有份设计的{{tsl|en|Land Rover Defender#Td5 engine|路虎卫士}}<ref name="ITV-service">{{Cite web |url=https://www.itv.com/news/2021-04-10/duke-of-edinburghs-funeral-to-take-place-on-saturday-17-april |title=Duke of Edinburgh's funeral to take place on Saturday 17 April |work=ITV |date=2021-04-10 |access-date=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410185807/https://www.itv.com/news/2021-04-10/duke-of-edinburghs-funeral-to-take-place-on-saturday-17-april |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC-service" /><ref name="bespoke">{{cite web |last=Coles |first=Any |url=https://news.sky.com/story/prince-philip-bespoke-land-rover-hearse-designed-by-duke-of-edinburgh-revealed-ahead-of-funeral-12276173 |title=Prince Philip: Bespoke Land Rover hearse designed by Duke of Edinburgh revealed ahead of funeral |work=Sky News |date=2021-04-15 |access-date=2021-04-15 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417110619/https://news.sky.com/story/prince-philip-bespoke-land-rover-hearse-designed-by-duke-of-edinburgh-revealed-ahead-of-funeral-12276173 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后灵柩从四方亭离开，送葬队伍依次为[[英国御林军|皇家近衛騎兵]]、擲彈兵衛隊及与亲王有關係的军事部队<ref name="Queen-Bentley">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56694327|title=Prince Philip funeral: Plans, timings and TV coverage|work=BBC News|date=2021-04-16|accessdate=2021-04-16|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417100835/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56694327|dead-url=no}}</ref>。灵柩覆盖着亲王个人的旗帜，旗帜上面是亲王的海军[[大盤帽|大盤帽]]和佩剑，配以白玫瑰和百合花，上附女王写的字条<ref name="ITV-service" /><ref name="BBC-service" /><ref>{{cite web |last1=Gariano |first1=Francesca |title=Queen Elizabeth says goodbye to Prince Philip with a note laid on his casket |url=https://www.today.com/news/queen-elizabeth-says-goodbye-prince-philip-note-t215441 |website=Today |access-date=2021-04-17 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417194708/https://www.today.com/news/queen-elizabeth-says-goodbye-prince-philip-note-t215441 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。队列从四方形前进到马蹄回廊（Horseshoe Cloister），由[[掷弹兵卫队|掷弹兵卫队]]军乐团打头阵，军队指挥官和参谋长紧随其后<ref name="ITV-service" /><ref name="BBC-service" /><ref name="Monarchy-Funeral">{{Cite web |url=https://www.royal.uk/funeral-duke-edinburgh-0 |title=Funeral of The Duke of Edinburgh |work=The Royal Family |date=2021-04-10 |access-date=2021-04-10 |archive-date=2021-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418001327/https://www.royal.uk/funeral-duke-edinburgh-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

亲王的子嗣、女婿及家政人员走在灵柩后面<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.sky.com/story/prince-philip-the-30-guests-attending-the-duke-of-edinburghs-funeral-have-been-announced-12276214|title=Prince Philip: The 30 guests attending the Duke of Edinburgh's funeral have been announced|work=Sky News|date=2021-04-15|accessdate=2021-04-15|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417142939/https://news.sky.com/story/prince-philip-the-30-guests-attending-the-duke-of-edinburghs-funeral-have-been-announced-12276214|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56761074|title=Prince Philip: Duke's four children to walk alongside coffin at funeral|work=BBC News|date=2021-04-15|accessdate=2021-04-15|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417180956/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56761074|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在他们面前的是坐在{{tsl|en|Bentley State Limousine|宾利豪华礼车}}的女王<ref name="Queen-Bentley"/>。[[英国皇家海军|皇家海军]]、皇家海军陆战队、{{tsl|en|Highlanders (Seaforth, Gordons and Camerons)|高地人 (海福斯、戈登斯和喀麦隆)|苏格兰皇家军团第4营高地人}}和[[英国皇家空军|皇家空军]]也在队伍中<ref name="Queen-Bentley"/>。{{tsl|en|King's Troop, Royal Horse Artillery|皇家马炮兵国王部队}}鸣枪数分钟<ref name="Monarchy-Funeral" />。

八名[[皇家海军陆战队|皇家海军陆战队]]的扶灵士兵将灵柩放置在西侧台阶，皇家近衛騎兵列队在旁<ref name="ITV-service" />。下午2点53分，步兵团仪仗队演奏[[英国国歌|英国国歌]]，皇家海军在旁吹奏风笛，其后全国默哀3分钟<ref name="Queen-Bentley"/>。约730名军人出现在温莎城堡，其中有四支军乐团<ref name="rehearsals">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56746947|title=Prince Philip: Rehearsals take place for Duke of Edinburgh's funeral|work=BBC News|date=2021-04-14|accessdate=2021-04-14|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417171757/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56746947|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Dean of Windsor|温莎教长}}{{tsl|en|David Conner (bishop)|戴维·康纳}}和[[坎特伯雷大主教|坎特伯雷大主教]][[贾斯汀·韦尔比|贾斯汀·韦尔比]]主持丧礼仪式<ref name="BBC-service" />。礼拜堂祭坛的垫子绣着亲王的各个纹章，包括英国及[[英联邦国家|英联邦国家]]授予的奖项和装饰、[[英国陆军元帅列表|陆军元帅]]權杖、皇家空军机翼、丹麦的{{tsl|en|Order of the Elephant|大象勳章}}和希腊的[[希腊救世主勋章|救世主勋章]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56694327|title=Prince Philip funeral: What are the plans and timings?|date=2021-04-15|accessdate=2021-04-15|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417100835/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56694327|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/15/funeral-rehearsal-shows-first-sighting-of-land-rover-prince-philip-helped-design|title=Funeral rehearsal shows first sighting of Land Rover Prince Philip helped design|work=The Guardian|first=Caroline|last=Davies|date=2021-04-15|accessdate=2021-04-15|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417024150/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/apr/15/funeral-rehearsal-shows-first-sighting-of-land-rover-prince-philip-helped-design|dead-url=no}}</ref>。仪式期间，四名歌手演唱简化的合唱歌曲<ref name="Sky-Alone">{{cite web|url=https://news.sky.com/story/william-and-harry-to-walk-separately-and-queen-to-sit-alone-at-prince-philips-funeral-12276355|title=Prince Philip: William and Harry to walk separately as details of Duke of Edinburgh's funeral procession revealed|work=Sky News|date=2021-04-15|accessdate=2021-04-15|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416223515/https://news.sky.com/story/william-and-harry-to-walk-separately-and-queen-to-sit-alone-at-prince-philips-funeral-12276355|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

按照亲王的遗愿，仪式不设[[布道|布道]]或{{tsl|en|Eulogy|颂词}}<ref name="Service-Chapel">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56779068|title=Prince Philip: Funeral to celebrate 'unwavering loyalty' to the Queen|date=2021-04-16|accessdate=2021-04-16|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417223951/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56779068|dead-url=no}}</ref>。仪式强调了亲王与皇家海军的联系及对海洋的热爱<ref name="Service-Chapel"/>。丧礼开头的合唱歌曲为[[威廉·克罗夫特|威廉·克罗夫特]]创作的《丧礼进行曲》（''Funeral Sentences''）<ref name="Service-Sky">{{cite web|url=https://news.sky.com/story/prince-philip-order-of-service-for-duke-of-edinburghs-funeral-12277419|title=Prince Philip: Order of service for Duke of Edinburgh's funeral|work=Sky News|date=2021-04-16|accessdate=2021-04-16|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418000057/https://news.sky.com/story/prince-philip-order-of-service-for-duke-of-edinburghs-funeral-12277419|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

温莎教长先诵读《[[便西拉智訓|便西拉智訓]]》第43章第11到26节，之后[[坎特伯雷大主教|坎特伯雷大主教]]诵读《[[约翰福音|约翰福音]]》第11章第21到27节<ref name="Service-Sky"/>。{{tsl|en|William Lovelady|威廉·洛夫拉迪}}受亲王委托，为《{{tsl|en|Psalm 104|诗篇104}}》的演唱伴奏<ref name="Service-Sky"/><ref>{{cite news|last=Roberts|first=Lizzie|date=2021-04-17|title=All the music from Prince Philip's funeral, including two pieces written at his request|work=The Telegraph|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/royal-family/2021/04/17/harmonious-farewell-music-duke-edinburghs-funeral/|access-date=2021-04-17|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417230818/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/royal-family/2021/04/17/harmonious-farewell-music-duke-edinburghs-funeral/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。仪式上的[[赞美诗|赞美诗]]包括通常用来赞美海员的《{{tsl|en|Eternal Father, Strong to Save|永恒圣父，恩能无边}}》、《{{tsl|en|Jubilate Deo (Britten)|欢呼颂}}》（由亲王指定）和《{{tsl|en|Kontakion|集禱頌}}》，由{{tsl|en|Walter Parratt|沃尔特·帕拉特}}爵士配乐<ref name="Service-Sky"/>。温莎教长赞扬亲王“坚定不移地忠诚于”女王，忠诚服务国家和英联邦<ref name="Service-Chapel"/>。教长也在灵柩落入皇家墓室（Royal Vault）时表达赞扬，同时[[皇家苏格兰兵团|皇家苏格兰兵团]]吹号手吹奏哀乐，从北奎尔走廊（North Quire Aisle）前往教长回廊（Dean's Cloister）。仪式以{{tsl|en|Garter King at Arms|嘉德纹章官}}{{tsl|en|Thomas Woodcock (officer of arms)|托马斯·伍德科克}}布告公爵的名号和头衔、《[[最后岗位|最后岗位]]》、坎特伯雷大主教祝祷、《{{tsl|en|Reveille|起床號}}》和英国国歌结束<ref name="Service-Sky"/>。

亲王将葬於圣乔治礼拜堂的皇家墓室<ref>{{cite web |title=Prince Philip: Royal Family honours duke's 'humour and humanity' |work=BBC News |date=2021-04-17 |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-56779068 |access-date=2021-04-17 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417205233/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-56779068 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ITV-service" /><ref name="BBC-service" />。若女王於日后驾崩，亲王的遗体将移送到圣乔治礼拜堂的国王乔治六世纪念教堂（King George VI Memorial Chapel），一同合葬<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/royal-family/prince-philip-death-buried-where-b1830560.html|title=Where will Prince Philip be buried?|work=The Independent|first=Olivia|last=Petter|first2=Ellie|last2=Abraham|date=2021-04-13|accessdate=2021-04-14|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416170755/https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/royal-family/prince-philip-death-buried-where-b1830560.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

